mxCell.value: Alerts for all nodes are sent by Netdata cloud

Netdata agents (parents)
- 2 year retention for all children with additional storage 
  configured for DBENGINE
- Each parent pushes metrics in real-time to the other parent
- Are connected to Netdata Cloud via the ACLK
  - Run health checks and send alert info
  - Send metadata about collected metrics
  - Respond to requests for data

Netdata agents (children) on each node
- No persistent metric retention (memory mode RAM)
- Not connected to Netdata cloud
- No agent dashboard
- Push metrics in real time to the first available parent
- Do not run health checks (no alert notifications)

- Real-time dashboards with long history
- Advanced grouping and filtering
- Advanced role based access
- Anomaly detection
- Custom dashboards
- Event feed
